headline: MarketAxess Announces Trading Volume Statistics for September and Third Quarter 2025
summary: NEW YORK, October 06, 2025--MarketAxess Holdings Inc. (Nasdaq: MKTX), the operator of a leading electronic trading platform for fixed-income securities, today announced trading volume and preliminary variable transaction fees per million ("FPM") for September 2025 and the third quarter ended September 30, 2025.1
